{"tid":1792202,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「把握機會」學杜魯多搭單貿易協議 將雙普選加入為簽成協議條件","createTime":"2019-12-21T12:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T13:00:34.000Z","uid":156109,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f4d110a334ea13ace7c8e8ce9c35a49ec5dabd35","tid":1792202,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T12:41:19.000Z","msg":"去開遊行集會就知道 最重要既訴求亦係最少人強調既訴求－－雙真普選<br />\n唯有呢樣先係打開其他訴求既鎖匙 先至有得選到代表自己既政府<br />\n不過D人覺得太難達成 難過獨立調查就暫且skip住先<br />\n依家正值中美貿易 加上人權法同馬格尼茲法既助攻下 係迫使中共俾香港人真普選既最佳時刻 點樣做呢？ 可以參考下加拿大總理杜魯多既做法<br />\n要求美國將釋放兩位加拿大公民作為同中國簽成貿易協議既條件<br />\n其實香港人一樣可以咁做 中國想同美國達成協議<br />\n就必先將真普選加入去協議條件<br />\n依家係中國最弱最被動既時候 一錯過左就冇架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6af4e88a31f55f22e8cc32f8123dafd65ea698","tid":1792202,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T12:43:03.000Z","msg":"【行動po】【求推】點解1223去稅局 連登冇人講？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1792093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1792093</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3Amr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=abce21c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3Amr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=9e71090f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"55bfe96e7edc789cabacdaa304ff782c7d2977cc","tid":1792202,"uid":156109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"r